# 🗺️ NexaKing (NXK) Roadmap

**Built with transparency. No overpromises. No hype.**  
Our progress is driven by real actions — not speculative deadlines. All steps below are either completed, in progress, or upcoming, and updated as we grow.

---

## ✅ Phase 1 – Foundation Setup  
**_Completed_**
- ✅ Official website launched: [nexaking.w3rooster.com](https://nexaking.w3rooster.com)
- ✅ ENS domain registered: `nexaking.eth`
- ✅ Social media profiles created under W3Rooster
- ✅ SEO indexing, JSON-LD, and search engine setup
- ✅ Airdrop form built using Tally.so (with anti-bot filtering)
- ✅ Jetpack & Buffer automation for cross-platform posting

---

## 🚧 Phase 2 – Token Launch & Airdrop Activation  
**_Currently in Progress_**
- ⏳ Deploy NXK token on Ethereum mainnet
- ⏳ Verify contract on Etherscan and publish token info
- ⏳ Add and lock liquidity on Uniswap
- ⏳ Share official links (Uniswap, Etherscan, DexTools)
- ⏳ Launch public airdrop (wallet + social tasks)
- ⏳ Announce launch across X, Telegram, and Discord

---

## 🔜 Phase 3 – Ecosystem Growth & Community Actions  
**_Upcoming Plans_**
- 🔍 Validate airdrop wallets and remove bots/duplicates
- 🎁 Distribute NXK airdrop to eligible users
- 📢 Begin AI-focused content and transparent updates
- 🌉 Explore multi-chain deployment (Base, Solana, BNB Chain)
- 📊 Evaluate NXK leaderboard or community tracker options
- 🗳️ Test lightweight governance tools for token holders

